OL,3,CYoung golfer aims to raise #100,000 in
OL,4,Cmemory of dad who died after transplant
OL,6,FKatie Cole went to meet the boy
OL,7,Fpreparing to tee off and break a world
OL,8,Frecord
OL,10,FA 7-year-old boy is on course to raise
OL,11,F#100,000 in memory of his dad who died
OL,12,Ffollowing a heart transplant.
OL,14,FGeorge Hughes, from Wigan, was just 18
OL,15,Fmonths old when his dad Dave had a
OL,16,Fheart transplant at the Freeman
OL,17,FHospital in Newcastle in May 2018.
OL,18,FSadly, complications led to Dave
OL,19,Fpassing away 11 weeks later.
