OL,6,FDuring that short time, the Hughes
OL,7,Ffamily were supported by the Freeman
OL,8,FHeart and Lung Transplant Association
OL,9,Fwhich helped them with accommodation,
OL,10,Ftravel and emotional support.
OL,12,FGeorge's mum Louise Hughes, who
OL,13,Fmarried Dave at the Freeman Hospital,
OL,14,Fstarted fundraising with George in
OL,15,F2019.
