OL,3,CYoung golfer aims to raise #100,000 in
OL,4,Cmemory of dad who died after transplant
OL,6,FMrs Hughes said: " We're hoping to get
OL,7,Fto the #100,000 mark this year. We are
OL,8,Fup to #88,000 so far and all the money
OL,9,Fgoes towards helping transplant
OL,10,Ffamilies in Newcastle. It's not just
OL,11,FNewcastle they are based, it's all
OL,12,Fover the country.
OL,14,F"It was the little things like they
OL,15,Fwould call and say let me pay your
OL,16,Fpetrol because we were back and forth
OL,17,Ffrom Newcastle to Wigan and that was a
OL,18,Flot of money.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
