OL,3,CYoung golfer aims to raise #100,000 in
OL,4,Cmemory of dad who died after transplant
OL,6,F"You could ask them for anything you
OL,7,Fwant and it wasn't just about the
OL,8,Fmoney either, the people who run it
OL,9,Fare all transplant patients and
OL,10,Ffamilies so they know the situation."
OL,12,FGeorge is hoping to set a world record
OL,13,Fby playing five rounds of golf in five
OL,14,Fdifferent countries in 24 hours. He
OL,15,Fwill tee off in Ireland on 20 June and
OL,16,Faims to finish the following day in
OL,17,FWales.
OL,19,FHe will also play on courses in
OL,20,FScotland, Ireland and in Cheshire in
OL,21,FEngland.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
