OL,3,CYoung golfer aims to raise #100,000 in
OL,4,Cmemory of dad who died after transplant
OL,6,FGeorge will be supported on the golf
OL,7,Fcourse by his grandfather Tony
OL,8,FSedgwick who said: "I feel like the
OL,9,Fluckiest grandad in the world because
OL,10,FI get to play golf with George who
OL,11,Floves the sport and plays in all
OL,12,Fweathers.
OL,14,F"We are keeping Dave's memory alive.
OL,15,FGeorge and the family talk a lot about
OL,16,Ftransplants and organ donation is key.
