OL,3,CYoung golfer aims to raise #100,000 in
OL,4,Cmemory of dad who died after transplant
OL,6,F"People should talk about organ
OL,7,Fdonation, share your wishes, talk
OL,8,Fabout it with your family, you can
OL,9,Fsave so many lives and be a superhero
OL,10,Feven when you pass away."
OL,12,FAs well as fundraising, Louise Hughes
OL,13,Fwas so inspired by the nurses who
OL,14,Fcared for Dave that the year after he
OL,15,Fdied she started training to become a
OL,16,Fnurse.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
