OL,3,CYoung golfer aims to raise #100,000 in
OL,4,Cmemory of dad who died after transplant
OL,6,FShe said: "I'm now I'm a fully
OL,7,Fqualified nurse. I work at my local
OL,8,Fhospital here but my end goal would be
OL,9,Fto be a transplant nurse and that
OL,10,Fwould be very special to me. I feel I
OL,11,Fcould talk to the families because I
OL,12,Fknow what they are going through.
OL,13,FThat's my end goal eventually."
